anade.</Para></LeadPara></HandL><TailParas fid="td"><Para>The Curious Incident of the Dog In the Night-time plays at the Esplanade Theatre from March 29 to Apr 8. Tickets from Sistic.</Para></TailParas><Byline fid="by" index="field">Helmi Yusof , Page-To-Stage Success </Byline><Credit fid="cr" index="field"></Credit><Contact fid="ct" index="field"></Contact><Notes fid="rf" index="field"></Notes><Art fid="art" index="field">The Curious Incident of the Dog In the Night-time plays. </Art><Copyright fid="cy" index="field">(c) 2018 Singapore Press Holdings Limited </Copyright></Article></ArchiveDoc><AdocTOC adoctype="article"><Item size="0" ref="distdoc:archive/ArchiveDoc::Article" type="arttext"></Item><Item size="0" ref="distdoc:archive/InvertText" type="invtext"></Item></AdocTOC></DistDoc>

